  <h2>Data <%= title %></h2>
  <p class="mark">
It is my aim to encourage other people to make further research regarding video patterns and video learning environments. Hence, all stored data is accessible through a REST API in JSON format. There are three datasets:

* one about the design patterns that is structured by the pattern components,
* a second about all analysed video learning environments including a categorization and references to the patterns, and
* a structured description of images that are related to the former two datasets.
  
To get an impression about these datasets you can open on of the following link in your browser. </p>
  
